Artifacts are stored with timestamp metadata and indexed for fast retrieval.

Typical implementation requires only a small parsing layer:

Estimated implementation size:

~200–1000 LOC C

Responsibilities include:
	•	date parsing
	•	artifact lookup
	•	history ordering
	•	optional hash display

